<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink367">
<l>poriyaraik kōṅkiṉ poṉmaruḷ pacuvī</l>
<l>viriyiṇar vēṅkaiyoṭu vēṟupaṭa milaicci</l>
<l>viravumala raṇinta vēṉiṟ kāṉyāṟṟut</l>
<l>tēroṭu kuṟuka vantōṉ</l>
<l>pēroṭu puṇarntaṉ ṟaṉṉaiyiva ḷuyirē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O mother!  Her life is united with the name  </l>
<l>of the man who came closely in [his] chariot to the river </l>
<l>in the spring forest whose expanse is adorned with flowers, </l>
<l>wearing [a garland] of fresh gold-resembling blossoms </l>
<l>of the Kōṅkam trees with scorched trunks,  </l>
<l>mixed with [flower-]clusters of Vēṅkai. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
